<Vertical id="HiddenDemo" title="Hidden Block Demo">
  <Markdown id="hidden_example">
### Example: Hidden Context for AI

Hidden includes children in the content tree without displaying them. Content is accessible programmatically (e.g., by LLMs scanning the page) but invisible to users. Below, an LLM could access the hidden rubric when analyzing the response, but students only see the question and input:
  </Markdown>

  <Vertical id="essay_example">
    <Markdown id="question">Explain the water cycle.</Markdown>
    <Hidden>
      <Markdown id="rubric">
**Rubric (hidden from students):**
- Mentions evaporation, condensation, precipitation
- Describes cyclical nature
- Uses appropriate terminology
      </Markdown>
    </Hidden>
    <TextArea id="response" placeholder="Write your explanation..." rows="4" />
  </Vertical>

</Vertical>
